105
00:08:28.799 --> 00:08:30.551 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I unsealed Morn's will.</c.bg_transparent>

106
00:08:32.803 --> 00:08:34.138 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He left everything to you.</c.bg_transparent>

107
00:08:35.097 --> 00:08:38.976 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Me? He left everything to me?</c.bg_transparent>

108
00:08:39.185 --> 00:08:40.019 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's right.</c.bg_transparent>

109
00:08:42.772 --> 00:08:43.606 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Morn...</c.bg_transparent>

110
00:08:46.108 --> 00:08:48.778 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>dear, sweet Morn.</c.bg_transparent>

111
00:08:49.695 --> 00:08:50.530 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh...</c.bg_transparent>

112
00:09:03.334 --> 00:09:07.046 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The poor fool actually believed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you cared about him.</c.bg_transparent>

113
00:09:07.171 --> 00:09:08.005 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I did.</c.bg_transparent>

114
00:09:08.089 --> 00:09:10.258 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was up for hours</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>last night thinking about him.</c.bg_transparent>

115
00:09:10.466 --> 00:09:12.885 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Calculating his net worth, no doubt.</c.bg_transparent>

116
00:09:13.135 --> 00:09:14.929 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We spent a lot of time together, Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

117
00:09:15.221 --> 00:09:17.056 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We were obviously a lot closer</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>than I ever realized.</c.bg_transparent>

118
00:09:19.350 --> 00:09:20.977 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>His financial records.</c.bg_transparent>

119
00:09:24.772 --> 00:09:26.065 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is this some kind of joke?</c.bg_transparent>

120
00:09:26.274 --> 00:09:27.108 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do you mean?</c.bg_transparent>

121
00:09:27.525 --> 00:09:28.818 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>According to this, he was broke.</c.bg_transparent>

122
00:09:29.110 --> 00:09:30.194 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sarcastically ) No.</c.bg_transparent>

123
00:09:30.861 --> 00:09:32.321 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How can that be?</c.bg_transparent>

124
00:09:32.697 --> 00:09:34.448 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He paid his bar bill</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>at the end of every month.</c.bg_transparent>

125
00:09:34.615 --> 00:09:36.784 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That kind of money</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>must have come from somewhere.</c.bg_transparent>

126
00:09:37.243 --> 00:09:40.079 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, he did have his shipping business.</c.bg_transparent>

127
00:09:40.204 --> 00:09:44.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe all his assets</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>are tied up in inventory.</c.bg_transparent>

128
00:09:44.458 --> 00:09:46.711 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course. Inventory.</c.bg_transparent>

129
00:09:50.172 --> 00:09:54.051 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll unload everything,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and use the profits to...</c.bg_transparent>

130
00:09:54.969 --> 00:09:57.805 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Oh, what's that smell?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Your inheritance.</c.bg_transparent>

131
00:09:58.014 --> 00:10:00.516 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Livanian beets. Very ripe.</c.bg_transparent>

132
00:10:01.517 --> 00:10:03.019 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's in the rest of these?</c.bg_transparent>

133
00:10:03.269 --> 00:10:04.645 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>More beets.</c.bg_transparent>

134
00:10:05.187 --> 00:10:08.524 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's it? That's all he had?</c.bg_transparent>

135
00:10:08.608 --> 00:10:09.442 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm afraid so.</c.bg_transparent>

136
00:10:09.525 --> 00:10:10.776 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( gasps )</c.bg_transparent>

137
00:10:12.820 --> 00:10:17.658 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Except for the contents of his quarters.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe he spent all his money</c.bg_transparent>

138
00:10:17.742 --> 00:10:22.246 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-on furnishings and works of art.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>-Objets d'art.</i></c.bg_transparent>

139
00:10:22.413 --> 00:10:23.664 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course.</c.bg_transparent>

140
00:10:24.624 --> 00:10:26.626 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Objets d'art.</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent> Of course.</c.bg_transparent>

141
00:10:27.585 --> 00:10:29.712 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll hold an auction.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>People will pay a premium</c.bg_transparent>

142
00:10:29.795 --> 00:10:31.631 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to own something that used to be Morn's.</c.bg_transparent>

143
00:10:37.595 --> 00:10:39.472 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you sure these are the right quarters?</c.bg_transparent>

144
00:10:39.639 --> 00:10:40.473 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sure.</c.bg_transparent>

145
00:10:41.432 --> 00:10:42.308 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Figures.</c.bg_transparent>

146
00:10:44.352 --> 00:10:45.269 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's that?</c.bg_transparent>

147
00:10:46.145 --> 00:10:48.439 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That, I believe, is a matador.</c.bg_transparent>

148
00:10:48.856 --> 00:10:51.275 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No. That.</c.bg_transparent>

149
00:10:52.026 --> 00:10:53.736 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ODO: That's Morn's bed.</c.bg_transparent>

150
00:10:54.278 --> 00:10:55.363 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Morn slept in...</c.bg_transparent>

151
00:10:56.322 --> 00:10:57.698 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>-mud? -Hmm.</c.bg_transparent>

152
00:10:58.491 --> 00:11:00.951 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm told it's excellent for the skin.</c.bg_transparent>

153
00:11:05.164 --> 00:11:06.415 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thanks, Morn.</c.bg_transparent>

154
00:11:06.749 --> 00:11:08.084 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just what I always wanted.</c.bg_transparent>

155
00:11:09.126 --> 00:11:09.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( gasping )</c.bg_transparent>

156
00:11:13.589 --> 00:11:15.674 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What are you doing in my mud?</c.bg_transparent>

157
00:11:16.050 --> 00:11:21.097 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, I... I couldn't resist.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Morny and I had so many happy times here,</c.bg_transparent>

158
00:11:21.180 --> 00:11:26.143 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I just... I had to slip in.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry if I startled you.</c.bg_transparent>

159
00:11:26.352 --> 00:11:29.105 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I heard you coming in</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and I thought I'd better hide.</c.bg_transparent>

160
00:11:29.647 --> 00:11:30.481 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who are you?</c.bg_transparent>

161
00:11:30.564 --> 00:11:31.565 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Um...</c.bg_transparent>

162
00:11:32.441 --> 00:11:33.275 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Larell.</c.bg_transparent>

163
00:11:34.276 --> 00:11:36.570 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Morn's wife. Well, ex-wife.</c.bg_transparent>

164
00:11:37.029 --> 00:11:38.114 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Morn was married?</c.bg_transparent>

165
00:11:38.823 --> 00:11:39.698 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>To you?</c.bg_transparent>

166
00:11:39.990 --> 00:11:41.700 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>For two wonderful years.</c.bg_transparent>

167
00:11:42.535 --> 00:11:44.745 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You must be Quark.</c.bg_transparent>

168
00:11:44.954 --> 00:11:48.124 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Morny and I kept in touch</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>after we were separated.</c.bg_transparent>

169
00:11:48.499 --> 00:11:51.877 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He talked about you all the time.</c.bg_transparent>

170
00:11:53.379 --> 00:11:54.463 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's nice.</c.bg_transparent>

171
00:11:55.047 --> 00:11:57.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He told me that if anything</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>ever happened to him,</c.bg_transparent>

172
00:11:58.050 --> 00:12:00.928 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>he wanted you to have everything</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that was ever his.</c.bg_transparent>

173
00:12:02.680 --> 00:12:03.681 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Everything?</c.bg_transparent>

174
00:12:05.641 --> 00:12:06.642 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Everything.</c.bg_transparent>

175
00:12:09.770 --> 00:12:11.355 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, I'm glad you came by,</c.bg_transparent>

176
00:12:12.398 --> 00:12:15.818 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>because Morny didn't leave</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>me much of anything else.</c.bg_transparent>

177
00:12:16.569 --> 00:12:18.195 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why, I find that hard to believe.</c.bg_transparent>

178
00:12:18.362 --> 00:12:19.196 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( laughs )</c.bg_transparent>

179
00:12:19.905 --> 00:12:22.533 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm as disappointed as you are.</c.bg_transparent>

180
00:12:23.033 --> 00:12:24.118 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I happen to know</c.bg_transparent>

181
00:12:24.285 --> 00:12:28.038 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that he had quite</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a substantial retirement fund,</c.bg_transparent>

182
00:12:28.164 --> 00:12:30.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>one that could make two people</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>very comfortable.</c.bg_transparent>

183
00:12:33.002 --> 00:12:37.214 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you're partial to mud,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it's comfortable, all right.</c.bg_transparent>

184
00:12:37.798 --> 00:12:40.759 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm talking about the thousand bricks</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of gold-pressed latinum</c.bg_transparent>

185
00:12:40.885 --> 00:12:42.970 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>that he won in the Lissepian Lottery.</c.bg_transparent>

186
00:12:43.304 --> 00:12:45.306 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A thousand bricks?</c.bg_transparent>

187
00:12:45.389 --> 00:12:50.144 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mm-hmm. Now that he's gone, it's all ours.</c.bg_transparent>

188
00:13:02.114 --> 00:13:05.075 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( vacuum slurping )</c.bg_transparent>

189
00:13:17.546 --> 00:13:18.380 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What are you doing?</c.bg_transparent>

190
00:13:18.964 --> 00:13:21.509 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do you think?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm looking for the latinum.</c.bg_transparent>

191
00:13:22.885 --> 00:13:24.803 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You must know where he kept it.</c.bg_transparent>

192
00:13:26.138 --> 00:13:29.225 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't even know it existed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>until you told me.</c.bg_transparent>

193
00:13:33.687 --> 00:13:36.232 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, I'm sure it's somewhere</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on the station.</c.bg_transparent>

194
00:13:36.774 --> 00:13:38.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How do we know he didn't spend it already?</c.bg_transparent>

195
00:13:39.068 --> 00:13:41.278 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I told you, it was for his retirement.</c.bg_transparent>

196
00:13:41.987 --> 00:13:45.574 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Poor Morn.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>He never got a chance to enjoy it.</c.bg_transparent>

197
00:13:46.700 --> 00:13:48.118 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But that doesn't mean we can't.</c.bg_transparent>

198
00:13:49.578 --> 00:13:50.996 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know what you're doing.</c.bg_transparent>

199
00:13:52.331 --> 00:13:53.707 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What am I doing?</c.bg_transparent>

200
00:13:54.667 --> 00:13:56.502 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just so we're clear...</c.bg_transparent>

201
00:13:56.919 --> 00:13:58.921 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>the latinum's mine.</c.bg_transparent>

202
00:14:00.130 --> 00:14:04.552 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He may have left everything to you,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but I was his wife.</c.bg_transparent>

203
00:14:05.261 --> 00:14:09.014 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I could contest the will,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and tie you up in court for years.</c.bg_transparent>

204
00:14:09.682 --> 00:14:10.516 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe.</c.bg_transparent>

205
00:14:11.392 --> 00:14:14.186 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But there's no reason</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it has to come to that.</c.bg_transparent>

206
00:14:14.353 --> 00:14:17.022 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>After all, a thousand bricks is plenty</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for both of us.</c.bg_transparent>

207
00:14:18.357 --> 00:14:19.942 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It is a lot of money.</c.bg_transparent>

208
00:14:22.528 --> 00:14:27.950 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And as soon as we find it,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we'll take a nice long vacation together.</c.bg_transparent>

209
00:14:29.201 --> 00:14:31.662 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Morn would have wanted it that way.</c.bg_transparent>

210
00:14:31.745 --> 00:14:33.914 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course, he would have.</c.bg_transparent>

211
00:14:42.381 --> 00:14:45.843 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The latinum's not on the station.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I looked everywhere. Evade.</c.bg_transparent>

212
00:14:46.677 --> 00:14:49.555 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I even had my brother scan for it</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with the internal sensors.</c.bg_transparent>

213
00:14:49.805 --> 00:14:51.098 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, at least you have the painting.</c.bg_transparent>

214
00:14:51.307 --> 00:14:54.018 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, forget the painting.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I want that latinum.</c.bg_transparent>

215
00:14:54.643 --> 00:14:55.978 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you think it'll make you happy.</c.bg_transparent>

216
00:14:56.145 --> 00:14:56.979 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Confront.</c.bg_transparent>

217
00:14:57.563 --> 00:14:58.898 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Believe me, it will.</c.bg_transparent>

218
00:15:01.233 --> 00:15:03.277 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is the break I've been waiting for,</c.bg_transparent>

219
00:15:03.861 --> 00:15:05.696 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and it's been a long time in coming.</c.bg_transparent>

220
00:15:06.280 --> 00:15:09.366 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want Morn's money. I need Morn's money.</c.bg_transparent>

221
00:15:10.451 --> 00:15:11.577 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I deserve Morn's money.</c.bg_transparent>

222
00:15:13.495 --> 00:15:14.330 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your move.</c.bg_transparent>

223
00:15:17.041 --> 00:15:21.295 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Beautiful, isn't it?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>And the way it picks up the light.</c.bg_transparent>

224
00:15:22.630 --> 00:15:25.925 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wonder who came up with the idea</c.bg_transparent>
