225
00:15:26.008 --> 00:15:27.843 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>inside worthless bits of gold?</c.bg_transparent>

226
00:15:28.177 --> 00:15:30.387 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Probably someone who got</c.bg_transparent>
