227
00:15:30.512 --> 00:15:31.555 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>with an eyedropper.</c.bg_transparent>

228
00:15:32.097 --> 00:15:33.098 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you going to play or not?</c.bg_transparent>

229
00:15:37.728 --> 00:15:38.854 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Where do you think Morn put it all?</c.bg_transparent>

230
00:15:40.898 --> 00:15:42.566 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you find it, are you really</c.bg_transparent>
