<c.bg_transparent>I agreed to pay her ten percent</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>so she wouldn't tie me up in court.</c.bg_transparent>

232
00:15:45.861 --> 00:15:46.862 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's 100 bricks.</c.bg_transparent>

233
00:15:47.613 --> 00:15:48.530 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What could I do?</c.bg_transparent>

234
00:15:48.781 --> 00:15:49.615 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Retreat.</c.bg_transparent>

235
00:15:51.992 --> 00:15:54.787 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know, but there's something</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I don't like about this whole thing.</c.bg_transparent>

236
00:15:55.704 --> 00:15:56.997 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't trust this woman.</c.bg_transparent>

237
00:16:00.292 --> 00:16:03.837 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Neither do I, but... that doesn't mean</c.bg_transparent>

238
00:16:03.921 --> 00:16:04.964 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm going to keep her away from my lobes.</c.bg_transparent>

239
00:16:05.589 --> 00:16:08.634 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just keep your eyes open.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Don't be fooled by a pretty face.</c.bg_transparent>

240
00:16:08.926 --> 00:16:10.010 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not me.</c.bg_transparent>

241
00:16:10.678 --> 00:16:12.930 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course not. Acquire.</c.bg_transparent>

242
00:16:28.696 --> 00:16:29.613 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh...</c.bg_transparent>

243
00:16:31.573 --> 00:16:34.284 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What a pleasant surprise.</c.bg_transparent>

244
00:16:39.164 --> 00:16:40.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer, lights.</c.bg_transparent>

245
00:16:42.918 --> 00:16:46.171 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell me... you like surprises, Quark?</c.bg_transparent>

246
00:16:46.839 --> 00:16:48.173 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Only pleasant ones.</c.bg_transparent>

247
00:16:49.133 --> 00:16:51.010 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I like to think I'm pleasant.</c.bg_transparent>

248
00:16:51.135 --> 00:16:53.846 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-You think I'm pleasant?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Absolutely.</c.bg_transparent>

249
00:16:54.513 --> 00:16:58.851 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then I guess this qualifies</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as a pleasant surprise.</c.bg_transparent>

250
00:16:59.351 --> 00:17:00.644 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What are you doing in my quarters?</c.bg_transparent>

251
00:17:00.769 --> 00:17:01.729 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Waiting for you.</c.bg_transparent>

252
