254
00:17:11.822 --> 00:17:13.032 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Really? Was it nice?</c.bg_transparent>

255
00:17:13.198 --> 00:17:14.992 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It was lovely.</c.bg_transparent>

256
