<c.bg_transparent>I understand you inherited Morn's estate.</c.bg_transparent>

257
00:17:19.621 --> 00:17:20.456 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's right.</c.bg_transparent>

258
00:17:21.498 --> 00:17:24.126 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're business associates of Morn's.</c.bg_transparent>

259
00:17:24.710 --> 00:17:25.544 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your brother mentioned that.</c.bg_transparent>

260
00:17:26.045 --> 00:17:29.965 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He... borrowed some money from us,</c.bg_transparent>

261
00:17:30.090 --> 00:17:35.220 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and we'd like the estate</c.bg_transparent>
