262
00:17:35.637 --> 00:17:36.597 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Uh-huh.</c.bg_transparent>

263
00:17:37.473 --> 00:17:39.433 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How much money are we talking about?</c.bg_transparent>

264
00:17:39.933 --> 00:17:41.018 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh...</c.bg_transparent>

265
00:17:42.436 --> 00:17:46.523 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>One thousand bricks</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of gold-pressed latinum.</c.bg_transparent>

266
00:17:46.899 --> 00:17:49.193 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I had a feeling</c.bg_transparent>
