268
00:17:57.034 --> 00:17:58.702 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We shook hands.</c.bg_transparent>

269
00:17:59.620 --> 00:18:00.788 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We trusted Morn.</c.bg_transparent>

270
00:18:01.705 --> 00:18:07.836 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And I'm sure he'd want you...</c.bg_transparent>
