278
00:18:39.284 --> 00:18:40.202 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're not?</c.bg_transparent>

279
00:18:41.078 --> 00:18:44.414 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
