284
00:18:58.929 --> 00:19:00.013 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A percentage.</c.bg_transparent>

285
00:19:00.180 --> 00:19:01.014 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
