290
00:19:07.271 --> 00:19:08.230 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't like beets.</c.bg_transparent>

291
00:19:08.689 --> 00:19:09.523 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'll take 70.</c.bg_transparent>

292
00:19:09.606 --> 00:19:10.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Forty.</c.bg_transparent>

293
00:19:10.524 --> 00:19:13.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And because I can see</c.bg_transparent>
