294
00:19:13.819 --> 00:19:15.529 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm willing to part with this.</c.bg_transparent>

295
00:19:15.696 --> 00:19:18.615 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>One of Morn's most treasured possessions.</c.bg_transparent>

296
00:19:18.699 --> 00:19:20.409 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Beautiful, isn't it?</c.bg_transparent>

297
00:19:20.492 --> 00:19:22.619 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Very nice.</c.bg_transparent>

298
00:19:22.703 --> 00:19:23.996 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We can't take less than 60.</c.bg_transparent>

