<c.bg_transparent>-Fifty.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Sorry.</c.bg_transparent>

301
00:19:30.627 --> 00:19:31.670 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Fifty it is.</c.bg_transparent>

302
00:19:32.212 --> 00:19:36.300 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm glad we could come</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to an understanding.</c.bg_transparent>

303
00:19:36.967 --> 00:19:37.885 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Me, too.</c.bg_transparent>

304
00:19:38.260 --> 00:19:39.094 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( laughs )</c.bg_transparent>

305
00:19:42.181 --> 00:19:44.933 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'll be watching you, Quark.</c.bg_transparent>

306
00:19:46.018 --> 00:19:47.477 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't try anything.</c.bg_transparent>

307
00:19:47.936 --> 00:19:50.022 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Me? Don't be ridiculous.</c.bg_transparent>

308
00:20:05.996 --> 00:20:07.748 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do we have here?</c.bg_transparent>

309
00:20:12.920 --> 00:20:15.255 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer, what is this?</c.bg_transparent>

310
00:20:16.965 --> 00:20:19.718 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>COMPUTER: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>A claim slip</i></c.bg_transparent>
