320
00:20:52.793 --> 00:20:57.673 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>when your deputies wheel</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in my thousand bricks of latinum.</c.bg_transparent>

321
00:20:58.840 --> 00:21:01.176 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah, here we are. Thank you.</c.bg_transparent>

322
00:21:01.843 --> 00:21:03.095 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That can't be it.</c.bg_transparent>

323
00:21:03.929 --> 00:21:06.765 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Storage Locker 137.</c.bg_transparent>

324
