00:33:16.953 --> 00:33:19.205 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>someone broke into the Central Bank</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and made off with...</c.bg_transparent>

549
00:33:20.373 --> 00:33:23.376 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>One thousand bricks</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of gold-pressed latinum.</c.bg_transparent>

550
00:33:27.463 --> 00:33:28.548 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Wait a minute.</c.bg_transparent>

551
00:33:29.048 --> 00:33:32.510 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You expect me to believe</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that the four of you pulled that off?</c.bg_transparent>

552
00:33:32.885 --> 00:33:34.846 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There was five of us. Morn helped.</c.bg_transparent>

553
00:33:35.263 --> 00:33:37.807 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, but then he ran off with the latinum.</c.bg_transparent>

554
00:33:38.808 --> 00:33:40.309 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why did you take</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>so long to come after him?</c.bg_transparent>

555
00:33:40.601 --> 00:33:42.770 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Because we knew he'd stashed it</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>away somewhere</c.bg_transparent>

556
00:33:43.021 --> 00:33:45.106 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to wait for the statute</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of limitations to expire.</c.bg_transparent>

557
00:33:45.481 --> 00:33:46.899 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And it did, two weeks ago.</c.bg_transparent>

558
00:33:47.358 --> 00:33:49.527 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You see, we can't be prosecuted anymore.</c.bg_transparent>

559
00:33:50.319 --> 00:33:51.362 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So here we are.</c.bg_transparent>

560
00:33:51.696 --> 00:33:52.989 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The latinum's en route.</c.bg_transparent>

561
00:33:54.365 --> 00:33:58.619 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe we should just split it up</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and go our separate ways.</c.bg_transparent>

562
00:33:59.037 --> 00:34:00.121 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The voice of reason.</c.bg_transparent>

563
00:34:00.371 --> 00:34:01.289 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not you...</c.bg_transparent>

564
00:34:04.292 --> 00:34:05.126 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>us.</c.bg_transparent>

565
00:34:05.585 --> 00:34:07.170 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Krit's right. We don't need him anymore.</c.bg_transparent>

566
00:34:19.974 --> 00:34:21.142 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So what do we do with him?</c.bg_transparent>

567
00:34:21.559 --> 00:34:23.186 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>KRIT: It should look like an accident.</c.bg_transparent>

568
00:34:23.394 --> 00:34:26.189 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We don't want anyone asking questions.</c.bg_transparent>

569
00:34:26.314 --> 00:34:28.983 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Wait a minute. You can't kill me.</c.bg_transparent>

570
00:34:29.317 --> 00:34:31.319 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm the only one who can take</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>delivery of the latinum.</c.bg_transparent>

571
00:34:31.694 --> 00:34:32.862 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You need my thumb print.</c.bg_transparent>

572
00:34:33.654 --> 00:34:36.032 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you stand still,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>this won't hurt as much.</c.bg_transparent>

573
00:34:36.115 --> 00:34:36.991 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( screaming )</c.bg_transparent>

574
00:34:37.158 --> 00:34:38.576 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>HAIN: Ah, ah, ah, wait a minute.</c.bg_transparent>

575
00:34:39.619 --> 00:34:41.037 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do you propose, Nahsk?</c.bg_transparent>

576
00:34:41.454 --> 00:34:43.956 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That we walk into the Cargo Bay</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with his bloody thumb,</c.bg_transparent>

577
00:34:44.040 --> 00:34:45.374 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and ask for the latinum?</c.bg_transparent>

578
00:34:45.833 --> 00:34:46.793 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We need him.</c.bg_transparent>

579
00:34:56.928 --> 00:35:01.099 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The only question is,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what happens after he takes delivery?</c.bg_transparent>

580
00:35:04.811 --> 00:35:08.064 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We could split the latinum... five ways.</c.bg_transparent>

581
00:35:08.481 --> 00:35:11.192 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That is what you would</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have gotten if Morn was still alive.</c.bg_transparent>

582
00:35:11.275 --> 00:35:12.193 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's true.</c.bg_transparent>

583
00:35:13.319 --> 00:35:14.695 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Think of me as Morn.</c.bg_transparent>

584
00:35:15.321 --> 00:35:16.656 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't believe I just said that.</c.bg_transparent>

585
00:35:17.115 --> 00:35:19.033 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This isn't fair. We stole it.</c.bg_transparent>

586
00:35:19.117 --> 00:35:20.284 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He had nothing to do with it.</c.bg_transparent>

587
00:35:20.368 --> 00:35:22.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe not, but the bottom line</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is you need me.</c.bg_transparent>

588
00:35:24.330 --> 00:35:26.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A thousand bricks of latinum</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>split five ways...</c.bg_transparent>

589
00:35:30.753 --> 00:35:31.712 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>what do you think?</c.bg_transparent>

590
00:35:33.506 --> 00:35:34.841 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's still a lot of latinum.</c.bg_transparent>

591
00:35:35.883 --> 00:35:39.470 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's 250 bricks each.</c.bg_transparent>

592
00:35:41.264 --> 00:35:42.348 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So do we have a deal?</c.bg_transparent>

593
00:35:47.145 --> 00:35:48.896 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-All right.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-OK.</c.bg_transparent>

594
00:35:49.188 --> 00:35:52.233 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Bolian transport</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>arrives tomorrow at 1600.</c.bg_transparent>

595
00:35:53.025 --> 00:35:53.985 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'll meet at the cargo bay.</c.bg_transparent>

596
00:35:54.277 --> 00:35:55.778 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're staying together until it gets here.</c.bg_transparent>

597
00:35:56.028 --> 00:35:56.904 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We are?</c.bg_transparent>

598
00:35:56.988 --> 00:35:59.574 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't trust you, and I certainly</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>don't trust them.</c.bg_transparent>

599
00:35:59.991 --> 00:36:01.033 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I see your point.</c.bg_transparent>

600
00:36:01.576 --> 00:36:05.121 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But I have a bar to run.</c.bg_transparent>

601
00:36:08.207 --> 00:36:09.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All right.</c.bg_transparent>

602
00:36:14.505 --> 00:36:15.590 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>To your hospitality.</c.bg_transparent>

603
00:36:16.007 --> 00:36:17.091 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't mention it.</c.bg_transparent>

604
00:36:21.721 --> 00:36:23.055 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So this was Morn's favorite place?</c.bg_transparent>

605
00:36:24.098 --> 00:36:25.516 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He used to sit right there.</c.bg_transparent>

606
00:36:25.933 --> 00:36:30.605 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, that's not very smart</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>sitting with your back to the door.</c.bg_transparent>

607
00:36:30.897 --> 00:36:32.523 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He was the trusting type.</c.bg_transparent>

608
00:36:34.150 --> 00:36:35.484 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Which one of you killed him anyway?</c.bg_transparent>

609
00:36:37.278 --> 00:36:38.154 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It wasn't us.</c.bg_transparent>

610
00:36:40.865 --> 00:36:41.908 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Me neither.</c.bg_transparent>

611
00:36:43.618 --> 00:36:44.452 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't look at me.</c.bg_transparent>

612
00:36:45.745 --> 00:36:47.163 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then it really was an accident.</c.bg_transparent>

613
00:36:49.248 --> 00:36:52.543 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Poor Morny. He always had such bad luck.</c.bg_transparent>

614
00:36:58.883 --> 00:36:59.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Get rid of him.</c.bg_transparent>

615
00:37:03.471 --> 00:37:04.388 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're closed.</c.bg_transparent>

616
00:37:05.473 --> 00:37:06.724 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>At this hour?</c.bg_transparent>

617
00:37:09.227 --> 00:37:10.061 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Friends of Morn.</c.bg_transparent>

618
00:37:10.478 --> 00:37:12.772 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're... commiserating.</c.bg_transparent>

619
00:37:13.022 --> 00:37:14.232 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I see.</c.bg_transparent>

620
00:37:16.567 --> 00:37:18.611 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And how long are you going to be closed?</c.bg_transparent>

621
00:37:19.237 --> 00:37:23.074 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, until about 1600 hours tomorrow.</c.bg_transparent>

622
00:37:25.201 --> 00:37:26.702 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We have a lot to commiserate about.</c.bg_transparent>

623
00:37:27.703 --> 00:37:29.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I see.</c.bg_transparent>

624
00:37:37.171 --> 00:37:38.464 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Where were we?</c.bg_transparent>

625
00:37:47.098 --> 00:37:48.224 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There it is.</c.bg_transparent>

626
00:37:48.766 --> 00:37:49.809 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Right on time.</c.bg_transparent>

627
00:37:52.061 --> 00:37:52.979 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Uh...</c.bg_transparent>

628
00:37:53.312 --> 00:37:55.398 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I believe that's for me.</c.bg_transparent>

629
00:38:12.081 --> 00:38:13.457 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Open it.</c.bg_transparent>

630
00:38:25.386 --> 00:38:26.679 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh...</c.bg_transparent>

631
00:38:27.722 --> 00:38:29.515 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll count it.</c.bg_transparent>

632
00:38:30.057 --> 00:38:30.891 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh...</c.bg_transparent>

633
00:38:41.360 --> 00:38:42.611 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All right.</c.bg_transparent>

634
00:38:42.987 --> 00:38:44.947 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Somebody else count it.</c.bg_transparent>

635
00:38:45.031 --> 00:38:50.619 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Put it down, Hain. My brother may be slow,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but if you pull that trigger,</c.bg_transparent>

636
00:38:51.370 --> 00:38:52.621 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>he'll kill you.</c.bg_transparent>

637
00:38:54.123 --> 00:38:56.042 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not slow.</c.bg_transparent>

638
00:39:01.881 --> 00:39:03.132 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nahsk...</c.bg_transparent>

639
00:39:04.091 --> 00:39:05.801 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>what are you doing?</c.bg_transparent>

640
00:39:07.345 --> 00:39:08.262 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're family.</c.bg_transparent>

641
00:39:08.346 --> 00:39:11.474 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just put the gun down.</c.bg_transparent>

642
00:39:22.026 --> 00:39:24.153 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( weapons fire continues )</c.bg_transparent>

643
00:39:25.905 --> 00:39:26.989 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go ahead.</c.bg_transparent>

644
00:39:27.823 --> 00:39:29.492 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Kill each other.</c.bg_transparent>

645
00:39:30.910 --> 00:39:31.827 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh...</c.bg_transparent>

646
00:39:35.122 --> 00:39:37.249 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( gasps )</c.bg_transparent>

647
00:39:37.333 --> 00:39:39.585 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ODO: Security. Drop your weapons.</c.bg_transparent>

648
00:39:39.668 --> 00:39:41.587 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Huh?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-( weapons fire continues )</c.bg_transparent>

649
00:39:42.129 --> 00:39:44.799 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>ODO: This is your last warning.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I said drop them.</c.bg_transparent>

650
00:39:45.049 --> 00:39:45.925 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( weapon clatters to ground )</c.bg_transparent>

651
00:39:46.008 --> 00:39:47.009 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>LARELL: I surrender.</c.bg_transparent>

652
00:39:49.178 --> 00:39:50.930 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Take her to a holding cell.</c.bg_transparent>

653
00:39:51.138 --> 00:39:52.723 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Get the rest of them to the Infirmary.</c.bg_transparent>

654
00:40:00.689 --> 00:40:03.150 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah, there you are.</c.bg_transparent>

655
00:40:03.234 --> 00:40:04.485 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are they gone?</c.bg_transparent>

656
00:40:04.985 --> 00:40:07.988 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>From now on,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you'll be commiserating alone.</c.bg_transparent>

657
00:40:08.322 --> 00:40:10.866 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All your "friends" are going to prison.</c.bg_transparent>

658
00:40:11.534 --> 00:40:12.618 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>For how long?</c.bg_transparent>

659
00:40:13.244 --> 00:40:15.454 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Assault with intent to kill?</c.bg_transparent>

660
00:40:15.538 --> 00:40:16.455 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Long enough.</c.bg_transparent>

661
00:40:17.373 --> 00:40:18.999 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then it's mine.</c.bg_transparent>

662
00:40:19.375 --> 00:40:20.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All mine.</c.bg_transparent>

663
00:40:22.920 --> 00:40:25.005 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What you are about to hear</c.bg_transparent>

664
00:40:25.381 --> 00:40:29.009 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>is the most beautiful sound in the galaxy.</c.bg_transparent>

665
00:40:34.390 --> 00:40:36.016 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, that can't be.</c.bg_transparent>

666
00:40:36.475 --> 00:40:38.477 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's no latinum in these bricks.</c.bg_transparent>

667
00:40:38.561 --> 00:40:39.478 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What?</c.bg_transparent>

668
00:40:40.062 --> 00:40:43.399 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Someone's extracted all the latinum!</c.bg_transparent>

669
00:40:43.816 --> 00:40:46.193 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's nothing here but worthless gold.</c.bg_transparent>

670
00:40:46.277 --> 00:40:48.529 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And it's all yours.</c.bg_transparent>

671
00:40:48.612 --> 00:40:50.072 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chuckling )</c.bg_transparent>

672
00:40:51.115 --> 00:40:53.117 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No.</c.bg_transparent>

673
00:40:53.325 --> 00:40:56.912 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No! No!</c.bg_transparent>

674
00:41:12.595 --> 00:41:14.013 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunting )</c.bg_transparent>

675
00:41:14.096 --> 00:41:16.515 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quark? Quark?</c.bg_transparent>

676
00:41:16.599 --> 00:41:17.433 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What?</c.bg_transparent>

677
00:41:18.392 --> 00:41:19.685 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do you want?</c.bg_transparent>

678
00:41:20.019 --> 00:41:21.729 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's someone here to see you.</c.bg_transparent>

679
00:41:21.896 --> 00:41:24.690 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I thought you said</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they were all going to prison.</c.bg_transparent>

680
00:41:24.773 --> 00:41:26.233 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You'd better sit down.</c.bg_transparent>

681
00:41:30.029 --> 00:41:31.071 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Morn?</c.bg_transparent>

682
00:41:31.363 --> 00:41:32.656 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Alive and well.</c.bg_transparent>

683
00:41:33.699 --> 00:41:35.743 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Apparently, he faked his own death,</c.bg_transparent>

684
00:41:35.993 --> 00:41:38.454 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but I'll let him tell you all about it.</c.bg_transparent>

685
00:41:45.669 --> 00:41:46.879 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well?</c.bg_transparent>

686
00:41:47.087 --> 00:41:47.922 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No.</c.bg_transparent>

687
00:41:48.422 --> 00:41:49.965 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want to hear it.</c.bg_transparent>

688
00:41:50.257 --> 00:41:51.675 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not one word.</c.bg_transparent>

689
00:41:52.343 --> 00:41:53.636 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You set me up.</c.bg_transparent>

690
00:41:57.515 --> 00:41:59.934 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You left the latinum to me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>because you knew I would do</c.bg_transparent>

691
00:42:00.017 --> 00:42:02.186 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>whatever it would take</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to get my hands on it.</c.bg_transparent>

692
00:42:02.603 --> 00:42:04.230 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You figured I could keep the four of them</c.bg_transparent>

693
00:42:04.313 --> 00:42:06.941 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>off-balance long enough for them</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to turn on themselves.</c.bg_transparent>

694
00:42:07.024 --> 00:42:10.861 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This whole thing was a scam</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to get them off your back, wasn't it?</c.bg_transparent>

695
00:42:15.533 --> 00:42:16.700 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I could have been killed, you know.</c.bg_transparent>

696
00:42:24.708 --> 00:42:27.169 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And I thought we were friends.</c.bg_transparent>

697
00:42:32.550 --> 00:42:33.592 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have to admit...</c.bg_transparent>

698
00:42:34.260 --> 00:42:36.470 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't suspect for a minute.</c.bg_transparent>

699
00:42:37.096 --> 00:42:38.013 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell you the truth,</c.bg_transparent>

700
00:42:38.305 --> 00:42:41.058 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't think you had it in you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to pull off something like this.</c.bg_transparent>

701
00:42:41.433 --> 00:42:42.851 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I just have one question for you.</c.bg_transparent>

702
00:42:43.060 --> 00:42:44.144 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What happened to the latinum?</c.bg_transparent>

703
00:42:56.407 --> 00:42:59.743 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( gurgling burp )</c.bg_transparent>

704
00:43:05.082 --> 00:43:08.002 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course. Your second stomach.</c.bg_transparent>

705
00:43:10.921 --> 00:43:13.257 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You've been keeping it</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in your second stomach</c.bg_transparent>

706
00:43:13.340 --> 00:43:14.967 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>all these years?</c.bg_transparent>

707
00:43:17.011 --> 00:43:18.387 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's a lot of latinum.</c.bg_transparent>

708
00:43:18.470 --> 00:43:20.055 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No wonder your hair fell out.</c.bg_transparent>

709
00:43:26.979 --> 00:43:28.022 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>For me?</c.bg_transparent>

710
00:43:32.735 --> 00:43:38.616 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That must be 100 bricks worth.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know what to say.</c.bg_transparent>

711
00:43:39.575 --> 00:43:40.409 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thanks.</c.bg_transparent>

712
00:43:40.618 --> 00:43:43.037 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not that I didn't earn it</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>after all you put me through.</c.bg_transparent>

713
00:43:45.873 --> 00:43:48.876 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you ever want to set</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>me up again, feel free.</c.bg_transparent>

714
00:43:52.463 --> 00:43:53.464 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know...</c.bg_transparent>

715
00:43:55.257 --> 00:43:58.218 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>you and I should consider</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>doing business together.</c.bg_transparent>

716
00:43:58.552 --> 00:44:01.138 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Two enterprising gentlemen like us</c.bg_transparent>

717
00:44:01.305 --> 00:44:06.518 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>could do all right for ourselves.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Take that gold dust of yours...</c.bg_transparent>

718
00:44:08.062 --> 00:44:10.147 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>it doesn't have to be a total loss.</c.bg_transparent>

719
00:44:10.230 --> 00:44:12.399 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I hear there's some primitive cultures</c.bg_transparent>

720
00:44:12.483 --> 00:44:14.234 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>who consider it quite valuable.</c.bg_transparent>

